<h1 class="text-black text-center text-6xl font-bold">Medical Terminology</h1>
<h3 class="mx-48 my-12 text-bold text-gray-700 text-center">Medical Terminology provides members with the opportunity to gain knowledge and skills regarding prefixes,
  suffixes, word roots, as well as anatomy, physiology, pathophysiology and occupations related to the health
  field. This competitive event consists of a written test with tiebreaker questions and aims to inspire members to
  learn about terms used in health professions and health specialties.</h3>

